---
title: White Fish, Prawn & Veggie Bengali Curry with Garlic Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: If you’re looking for a cosy meal to add to the table, we can’t recommend this rich fish curry enough. Let the warm flavours of the Mumbai spice and coconut add an extra layer and you’ll be humming in bliss with every bite.

